{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Robots at Midnight is a retro-futuristic souls-like that takes place on Yob, a world now in ruins. Built as a luxury destination, the planet is overrun with dangers, challenging for any human to endure. Be home before Midnight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u3010Combat with Fluid Movement\u3011</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623040/extras/combat-steam.gif?t=1734579115\" />Harness the power of your space-gauntlet, known as The MITT, to boost, punch, and kick off enemies! Energetic movement options let you explore the world or get the upper hand in combat. Find your fighting style as you perfect your skills and strategy. Test your scrap \u201cmetal\u201d!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u3010Choose Your Challenge\u3011</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623040/extras/dyno-steam.gif?t=1734579115\" />Robots at Midnight offers a flexible challenge level for souls-curious and hardcore players alike.\u00a0In Hero mode, you will experience the action, story, and exploration of Yob at a more approachable pace.  For Masters, this mode offers a faster, more intense challenge to test your reflexes, determination and strategies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\u3010Explore and Uncover Hidden Lore\u3011</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623040/extras/lore-steam1.gif?t=1734579115\" />What would you do if you woke up in a completely new world?  Help Zoe discover what happened and learn more about the world of Yob.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623040/extras/all-shapes-sizes-steam.gif?t=1734579115\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To learn more about Robots at Midnight be sure to follow our socials, sign up for our newsletter, and join our Discord.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623040/extras/Finish-Line-Games-RAM-SteamAssets-CallToAction-Discord-Animated.gif?t=1734579115\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623040/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734579115","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623040/page.bg.jpg?t=1734579115","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623040/1aa9245c6102fad1c51ce8a3a24aebce9eda4f2f/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734579115","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623040/1aa9245c6102fad1c51ce8a3a24aebce9eda4f2f/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734579115","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<h1>Buzz</h1><p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623040/extras/IAB.jpg?t=1734579115\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623040/extras/paxrisingselect168x155.jpg?t=1734579115\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2623040/extras/goldenjoystick275x155.jpg?t=1734579115\" /><br><br>&quot;... grabs you right from the start.&quot; - LVLOne<br><br>&quot;...an engaging experience.&quot; - Lords of Gaming<br><br>&quot;You can always tell a boss means business when it comes with a subtitle.&quot; - Game Informer<br><br>\u201cCh